title: GameDay View - Will Cowboys upset Rams? Packers-Giants predictions; Sneaky good players;  Week-5 picks
itunes:title: GameDay View - Will Cowboys upset Rams? Packers-Giants predictions; Sneaky good players;  Week-5 picks
description:
The GameDay View Podcast begins with week 5 matchups between the Packers-Giants in London and the Ravens-Bengals on Sunday Night Football. Find out who thinks the Bengals will upset the Ravens in Baltimore. Hosts Patrick Claybon, Cynthia Frelund, and Gregg Rosenthal discuss the highly anticipated matchup between the Dallas Cowboys and Los Angeles Rams and then they dive into "more or less" - Will Aaron Rodgers have more or less than 230 passing yards against the Giants? Later, they each share a sneaky good player and then the podcast finishes up with final week-5 predictions.

The GameDay View Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
